modName: Nude Female Draugr and Dragon Priest
summary: As the name stands, all draugrs and dragon priests now have nude female appearance.
descriptionHtml:
So, first you will need to have any female body replacement mod installed. Theoretically it does not matter if it is CBBE or UNP or whatever other body shape. I am not sure if CHSBHC works: that is up to you to test. 

Draugrs should have the same stats as vanilla. However the dragon priests now have different stats because I changed their race and rescale the level (lv 150). 

Report bugs to me.
author: imagnus
